The paper discusses the challenges of incorporating human-like cognitive abilities into robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the efforts of robotics research communities to find a solution, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The mention of the Human Brain Project suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV) as well.
